        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-dark-green mb-3">Community</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600">Connect with fellow enthusiasts who share your passion. Build lasting friendships and enjoy social events with like-minded members.</p>
    </div>
    
