      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-dark-green mb-3">Technical Support</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600">Access expert advice, workshops, and technical resources. Many clubs maintain libraries of workshop manuals and parts catalogs.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
      <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-dark-green/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6 text-dark-green">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6.75 3v2.25M17.25 3v2.25M3 18.75V7.5a2.25 2.25 0 012.25-2.25h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 7.5v11.25m-18 0A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0021 18.75m-18 0v-7.5A2.25 2.25 0 015.25 9h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 11.25v7.5m-9-6h.008v.008H12v-.008zM12 15h.008v.008H12V15zm0 2.25h.008v.008H12v-.008zM9.75 15h.008v.008H9.75V15zm0 2.25h.008v.008H9.75v-.008zM7.5 15h.008v.008H7.5V15zm0 2.25h.008v.008H7.5v-.008zm6.75-4.5h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0 2.25h.008v.008h-.008V15zm0 2.25h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm2.25-4.5h.008v.008H16.5v-.008zm0 2.25h.008v.008H16.5V15z" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-dark-green mb-3">Events & Activities</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600">Participate in rallies, shows, tours, and social gatherings. Enjoy driving your classic in the company of other enthusiasts.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Newsletter Section -->
<div class="bg-dark-green text-white py-16">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif mb-4">Stay Updated</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">Subscribe to our newsletter for the latest news about classic car clubs, events, and community updates.</p>
      
      <form action="/api/subscribe" method="post" class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
        <input 
          type="email" 
          name="email" 
          placeholder="Your email address" 
          required
          class="flex-grow px-4 py-3 rounded bg-green-800/50 border border-green-700 text-white placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent"
        >
        <button 
          type="submit" 
          class="bg-accent hover:bg-accent-dark text-dark-green py-3 px-6 rounded uppercase text-sm tracking-wider font-serif transition duration-150"
        >
          Subscribe
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>